title: DungeonDragons 0.0.1.apk
description:
Inspired from the famous game,Flappy Bird we bring to you the most adorable,interesting and adventurous Flappy Dungeon Dragons. Lot of games like this but the best is always on the top. Flappy Dungeon Dragons is filled with Challenges. Lot of mountains ,terrains, fields and of course Dragons to play with. To help you we have Power ups which will astonishingly help you get through difficult times.Tap your Dragons to rise in the sky and go up. Make your way through the difficult paths of the mountain. This is an endless runner game. Shrink your Dragons or create a force field around your Dragons or even make your Dragons invisible,Its all there. We gave you new fields to explore and 11 new Dragons to glide your way through the Dungeon. Download your fun to the next level and pass your time with a blast. 
FLAPPY DUNGEON DRAGONS, its all what everyone wanted.
